subject: Tour de France (Bicycle Race)
Bicycles and Bicycling
lead_paragraph: For now, Dutch cyclist Kenny Robert Van Hummel has the honor of being the rider known as the Lantern Rouge, or the Red Lantern, which is the last-place rider in the Tour.
